HEADWORD: Statuesquely
<hw>Stat`u*esque"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a statuesque manner;
in a way suggestive of a statue; like a statue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A character <qex>statuesquely</qex> simple in its details.</q>
<rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Statuette</ent>⟦br⟧
